{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>This demo is a precursor to the events of DAWN (COMING SOON).</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> -<br> <br>In DAWN: CALM BEFORE THE STORM DEMO, you play as Trey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A handyman for the now powerless - and dead silent - facility that, you, now find yourself waking up alone in. <br> <br>With the keys needed for accessing the rest of the building being top-side, for now, you must venture into the nearby storage room, access what you can and don't forget to turn on your flashlight.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273270/extras/2321qdsa.png?t=1737248005\" /><br>  <br> You'll need it, for once you reach the roof; You soon realize this isn't just another ordinary shift - something happened. And all while Trey slept.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reach the roof, restore power to the building, take in your surroundings, familiarize yourself with controls, and enjoy the peace while it lasts.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>For soon, The DAWN will reveal itself. And you'll regret ever turning the lights back on.</u> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>WITNESS THE DAWN! A new horror stirs in The American West. It isn\u2019t an ordinary night. The storm outside was just the start. The wind. The rain. An omen of things to come. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i></i>---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>All rights reserved - Affinity Gameworks 2024.</i><span class=\"bb_strike\"><u></u></span> </p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3273270?t=1737248005","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273270/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737248005","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i